'''Glazed glucose pate''' was a delicacy enjoyed by [[Ugor/Legends|Ugors]]. It was extremely dense and made of sugar.<ref name="swg">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=item|Glazed Glucose Pate}}</ref> The chef droid [[L9-G8]] instructed the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] crew of the ''[[Bonderium]]'' to cook this dish for an Ugorian feast, in order to bribe [[ArrGack]] and [[GrrKack]] for admission to the [[Paradise system/Legends|Paradise system]].

